  "output_scope": {
    "ml_output_count": 10,
    "non_ml_actuators": [
      "lights"
    ],
    "notes": [
      "lights: pseudo-input lights_active (ML feature); relay via schedule/Nodeflow; safety thermal cutoff forces OFF; optional heat-assist policy; lamp heat watts in simulator config.",
      "fan: jedno wyj\u015bcie ML; kilka fizycznych wentylator\u00f3w \u2192 mapowanie w mostku sprz\u0119towym.",
      "irrigation_zone_N: 0\u20134 aktywnych stref (zones[N].irrigation.available); nieaktywne = available false, safe output 0."
    ]
  },
  "independence_rules": [
    "soil_moisture_pct and soil_temperature_c per zone are unrelated inputs (e.g. moisture probe + DS18B20 in pot).",
    "nutrient_solution_temperature_c is separate from soil_temperature_c (DS18B20 in nutrient tank / feed line).",
    "Compare solution vs soil temp in safety before irrigation \u2014 avoid cold nutrient on warm substrate."
  ],
